{"id": 1116, "genre": 1001, "title": "你今年有过哪些“消费升级”的尝试？", "description": "给“买买买”取一个超凡脱俗的名字。（题图来自： Leo Natsume）", "record_count": 3188, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160718145824iTp8XkGZbM50UNAa.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-19T03:01:09Z", "options": [{"id": 99840, "content": "帝都，从租房到买房。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684642}, {"id": 99841, "content": "iPhone 6 Plus换到了LG G5。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673800}, {"id": 100097, "content": "换新笔啦，下载新效率类app啦～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425416}, {"id": 99842, "content": "洗面奶从超市货换成了cpb……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678342}, {"id": 99843, "content": "买了双美国来的鞋子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683525}, {"id": 99845, "content": "参加了当爷的见面会", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684646}, {"id": 100101, "content": "买了一副单车扑克牌没事玩玩魔术", "image": "img/option/option/20160720213727gWEGShFXa9puDvZb", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277441}, {"id": 99846, "content": "iPhone6s换成了Nokia n9……我也无法理解", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662414}, {"id": 99847, "content": "对比聚美，淘宝，唯品会分别下单数额，照顾消费较低的APP，使其保持均衡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653221}, {"id": 99848, "content": "香水从倩碧到迪奥到香奈儿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671086}, {"id": 99849, "content": "把普通上衣和裙换成了JK制服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684663}, {"id": 99850, "content": "从一般的显卡升级到了GTX1070 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493335}, {"id": 104458, "content": "淘宝爆款换成原单\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703141}, {"id": 99851, "content": "把卡西欧换成浪琴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258437}, {"id": 104459, "content": "iPhone6s 64g 升级成 6sp 128g\n刷朋友圈 升级成看书看报\n葛优躺 升级成 跑步和keep\n各种外卖 升级成 自己动手做新鲜饭\n淘宝爆款 升级成 高品质原单和设计\n 不拘小节 升级成 美甲和小饰品装点\n公交车  升级成  出租车\n普通活动 升级成 品牌发布会\n", "image": "img/option/option/20160805063638h3GtJrb7XOiuWKN2.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703141}, {"id": 99852, "content": "交了个男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684679}, {"id": 99854, "content": "买了本书…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655461}, {"id": 100622, "content": "想把用了5、6年的笔记本换成macbook高配版（哎…只能想想，工作还没稳定?）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688252}, {"id": 99855, "content": "在德国买了一把wmf的刀……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 459839}, {"id": 101648, "content": "发现网络上的连载小说大同小异，开始转向读纸质书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690329}, {"id": 103184, "content": "等年底新macbook pro", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476254}, {"id": 99857, "content": "升级了我的电脑，毕竟是吃饭的家伙", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684717}, {"id": 99858, "content": "把美宝莲的口红换成了香奈儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684718}, {"id": 99859, "content": "去日本买了个made   in   chian的帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404446}, {"id": 99862, "content": "把三星手机换成了三星s7", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285820}, {"id": 99863, "content": "给手机网游充了很多钱，我的第一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671459}, {"id": 99864, "content": "迅雷会员", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 538346}, {"id": 99865, "content": "抛弃流水线产品、能专属定制的尽量个性化。比如一支金属材质的中性笔、一件Nike的T-shirt、一款苹果皮···", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453493}, {"id": 99866, "content": "换了老婆.算不算.", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115474}, {"id": 99867, "content": "一顿饭500以下太便宜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684746}, {"id": 99868, "content": "电脑也能用脑残粉色了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404003}, {"id": 99869, "content": "买了双鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617678}, {"id": 99870, "content": "一切婴儿用品海淘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684753}, {"id": 99872, "content": "把手动档换成自动档……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197532}, {"id": 100128, "content": "护肤品从国内大牌到了国外", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637396}, {"id": 99873, "content": "等最新的Macbookpro！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230259}, {"id": 99874, "content": "以前总是爱玩游戏。控制不了自己。现在好多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684764}, {"id": 99875, "content": "开始吃进口麦片这种食品.", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684765}, {"id": 99876, "content": "苏格兰狗开始吃加拿大狗粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684772}, {"id": 99877, "content": "粉底从美宝莲到迪奥", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 618538}, {"id": 100133, "content": "从此开始养孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686127}, {"id": 99878, "content": "买了限量版的英文三体……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684776}, {"id": 99879, "content": "买来有史以来最贵的鞋子！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 664575}, {"id": 99881, "content": "耳机从beats换成了bose", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684784}, {"id": 99882, "content": "喝voss", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 584951}, {"id": 99883, "content": "终于又买了人生第二双吐血的球鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682083}, {"id": 99884, "content": "打车变成了家常便饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437319}, {"id": 99887, "content": "买了一双Nike鞋...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684820}, {"id": 99890, "content": "四线城市月入12000，结果信用卡差点还不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594232}, {"id": 99891, "content": "呵呵哒", "image": "img/option/option/20160719231430Zmw6rn1QscLND8oz.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684831}]}